abusinessl: Muang Thai Insurance PCL is a Thailand-based company engaged in the provision of non-life insurance business. Its non-life insurance can be categorized into motor and non-motor products. The motor insurance products include compulsory and voluntary insurance. The non-motor insurance products include property insurance, such as fire insurance and terrorism insurance; marine cargo insurance, such as domestic cargo insurance and fleet insurance; engineering insurance, such as machinery insurance and electronic equipment insurance; personal accident and health insurance, including individual and group insurance; special products, such as gem and gold insurance, as well as liability insurance. The Company was founded in 1951 and is located in Bangkok, Thailand.
